text: A MOvE to stop Mr. Gaitskell from nominating any more Labour life Peers is to be made at a meeting of Labour OM Ps tomorrow. Mr. Michael Foot has put down a resolution on the subject and he is to be backed by Mr. Will Griffiths, OM P for Manchester Exchange.
